# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
The approach lies in the problem if u see carefully we will always add two consecutive element when we do partion so if we store all the sum of two consecutive element and take k-1 max summations and k-1 min summations will give particular max and min score. 
the result will be their difference.

